  "style_summary_en": "Michelin 2-star.\n\nChef Takemasa Shinohara weaves his rural Shiga roots and family recipes into every course.\nHassun (八寸) highlights childhood memories from Shiga.\nIntegrates menus from Japan's five imperial ceremonies and annual traditions.\nApproximately 3-hour course, ¥35,000.",
  "style_summary_jp": "ミシュラン2つ星。\n\nシェフ篠原武将が故郷滋賀の田舎と父の家族レシピを深く反映。\n八寸コース — 幼少期の滋賀の思い出。\n日本五大皇室儀礼・年中行事メニューを統合。\n約3時間コース、¥35,000。",
  "holistic_signature_en": "Authentic Tokyo kaiseki.\nCultural storyteller tone + fully seasonal rotation.",
  "holistic_signature_jp": "東京正統懐石。\n日本文化の伝達者トーン + 季節ごとの完全変動。"
